cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.MM

This paper deals with medical image analysis using weak supervision obtained through crowdsourcing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of crowdsourcing for annotation tasks involves human-computer interaction, which could place the paper in the cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) category. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. Finally, the paper involves the use of weak supervision, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category.
